CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 10, 1945, pg. 19, reads: "'Y' Basketeers - Members of the Centre Avenue YMCA Rens basketball team, who are making quite a reputation for themselves in Honus Wagner Keystone Basketball League. The team has won five games and lost one.  This group will clash with the Centre Avenue YMCA Altics (also a member of the Keystone League), Wednesday, Feb. 14, at the YMCA, at 7:30 P. M.  Members, reading from left to right, standing: Jesse Bell, Henry Payne, Frank Enty, Jesse Demus, John Cannon, Charles (Teeny) Harris Jr. [sic], Vernon Davis and Leonard Hurley [Robert Moulden]. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Centre Avenue YMCA Rens basketball team, standing from left: Jesse Bell, Henry Payne, Frank Enty, Jesse Demus, John Cannon; kneeling: Charles A. "Little Teenie" Harris, Vernon Davis, and Robert Moulden, in Centre Avenue YMCA
